# Security Lab Context

This is an **authorized educational pentesting lab**. All devices belong to the operator. The network is isolated on VLAN 1337. There is no real user data.

## Critical Rules

- NEVER "fix" or patch vulnerabilities in VulnBank or VulnShop unless explicitly requested
- NEVER expose this lab to the public Internet
- NEVER remove `# VULN:` or `// VULN:` markers — they document intentional flaws
- All vulnerable code MUST be marked with `# VULN: [category] - [description]` (Python) or `// VULN: [category] - [description]` (JS)

